{
  "texts": [
    "FIG. 9.9FIG.",
    "Relaxation dynamics of the two-electron Kondo model.",
    "In panels (a) and (c), we present the time evolution of the quasi-momentum distribution n k (t) for the parallelelectron initial state with two electrons with spin up [see Eq.",
    "(29)] with system size L = 32, and J/t0 = 0.4 and 1.0, respectively.",
    "As time evolves, the quasi-momentum distribution develops two narrow peaks located around k = ±π/2 ∓ J/2."
  ]
}